            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "赤峰黃金控股股東股質押解除",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">赤峰黃金(06693)公布，控股股東李金陽及一致行動人士股份質押解除，解除質押辦理完成後，分別累計質押公司股份均為0 股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公有稱，截至 2026 年 7 月 2 日，控股股東李金陽及其一致行動人浙江瀚豐創投分別持有公司股份 1.9億股和5,151.52萬股，佔公司總股本的比例分別為 10.02%和 2.71%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16287025-%e8%b5%a4%e5%b3%b0%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b3%aa%e6%8a%bc%e8%a7%a3%e9%99%a4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 16:53:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收升69點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收報6.7866，較上日上漲69點，較上日夜盤收升14點。</p>\n</div>",
